For like an ultra low budget, but higher privacy model, you can use GPT-401-mini from OpenAI.

00:13:02.979 --> 00:13:08.739
Before I went out of office five days ago, this was like the newest snappy model from

00:13:08.940 --> 00:13:09.940
OpenAI.

00:13:09.940 --> 00:13:15.539
And of course, five business days is like a decade in LLM time.

00:13:15.539 --> 00:13:18.940
Don't use LLAMA for now, sorry.

00:13:18.940 --> 00:13:24.179
If you want to keep track of this process where I'm trying to find some cheaper models

00:13:24.179 --> 00:13:28.820
and some local models that we could be running on our laptops to do these sorts of smaller

